{"word":"Cowardice","slug":"cowardice","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Cowardice</b> General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=37'>Lev 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=8'>Deu 20:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=30'>Deu 32:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=5'>Jos 7:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=23&verse=10'>Jos 23:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=15&verse=24'>Job 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=18&verse=11'>Job 18:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=28&verse=1'>Pro 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=29&verse=25'>Pro 29:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=51&verse=13'>Isa 51:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=6&verse=12'>Gal 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=16'>2Ti 4:16</a><br/><a href='S:Courage'>Courage</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Adam, in attempting to shift responsibility for his sin upon Eve<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=12'>Gen 3:12</a> <br/> - Abraham, in calling his wife his sister<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=19'>Gen 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=20&verse=12'>Gen 20:12</a> <br/> - Isaac, in calling his wife his sister<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=9'>Gen 26:9</a> <br/> - Jacob, in fleeing from Laban<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=31'>Gen 31:31</a> <br/> - Aaron, in yielding to the Israelites, when they demanded an idol<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=24'>Exo 32:24</a> <br/> - The ten spies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=28'>Num 13:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=33'>Num 13:33</a> <br/> - Israelites:<br/> b in fearing to attempt the conquest of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=5'>Num 14:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=28'>Deu 1:28</a><br/> b in the battle with the people of Ai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=5'>Jos 7:5</a><br/> b Fearing to meet Goliath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=24'>1Sa 17:24</a><br/> b Fearing to fight with the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=7'>1Sa 13:7</a><br/> - Twenty thousand of Gideon's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a> <br/> - Ephraimites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=9'>Psa 78:9</a> <br/> - Ephraimites and Manassehites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=18'>Jos 17:18</a> <br/> - Amoritish kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=16'>Jos 10:16</a> <br/> - Canaanites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=2&verse=11'>Jos 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=1'>Jos 5:1</a> <br/> - Samuel, fearing to obey God's command to anoint a king in Saul's stead<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=2'>1Sa 16:2</a> <br/> - David, in fleeing from Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=17'>2Sa 15:17</a> <br/> - Nicodemus, in coming to Jesus by night<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=2'>Joh 3:2</a> <br